A: X-coord in the overworld
B: Y-coord in the overworld
C: "Cursor", var holding position that the menu cursor should be in
D: Value of C from last loop/before a keypress
E: Exp
F: A+.1B of hidden treasure
G: V+1.W of hidden treasure
H: Current HP
I: Number of steps taken since last encounter (can't get an encounter before this number is 10)
J: "Jump" out of walking loop flag
K: Getkey var (1 if save+quit, -1 if quit without saving)
L: Level
M: World map size
N: New game flag. For use if intro is desired. If not, remove it from code.
o
p
Q: Can use town inn flag
R: Resilience level (defense)
S: Max enemy HP
T: Current enemy HP
U: "Update" F1 Menu options flag
V: Y-coord in the current overworld plot
W: X-coord in the current overworld plot
X: Escape success flag
Y: Double For( loop variable (used in map drawing)
Z: Quit from main menu flag, enemy type
Theta: For( loop variable
Str1: Used for displaying the first option in F1 menu
(list)SOLSV: Save file
L1: Temp var for treasure coords
